nodes.text: Mos Eisley Biolab was a biotechnology company based in Mos Eisley, on the planet Tatooine. Circa 1 ABY, the laboratory in Mos Eisley was ravaged and the scientists Bera Jeza and Derg Prantis were assassinated. Because of the relationship between Bera Jeza and the Crime lord Jabba Desilijic Tiure, Bib Fortuna hired a spacer to investigate the murders. Thanks to the help of Cale Herron, the investigation eventually led to the discovery of the Blackwing outbreak on Dathomir.
